// Self-contained workspace for the Grafana data source plugin. It is
// intentionally NOT part of the repo-root go.work: that workspace exists to
// resolve cross-imports between the infra/ controllers, which this plugin
// neither imports nor is imported by. Keeping it separate lets the plugin track
// the latest grafana-plugin-sdk-go (and the go version it needs) without
// forcing those dependency versions onto the infra modules.
go 1.26.4

use .
